document_data.mainbody:
Toll Street was a small road located in the city of Zhentil Keep during the mid-14 century DR.
Toll Street was located in Zhentil Keeps Common Quarter in the west section of the city. The road ran east to west in between Pain Street in the east and Dixon Street in the west. It measured  in length.
Several notable buildings were located along Toll Street where it intersected others streets. The Whipwalkers Cloak sat at its junction with Pain Street, and the business of the Celebrated Embalmer Morge at the junction with Dixon Street.
